001package org.consensusj.bitcoin.json.pojo.bitcore;
002
003import com.fasterxml.jackson.annotation.JsonProperty;
004import org.bitcoinj.base.Address;
005import org.bitcoinj.base.Coin;
006import org.bitcoinj.base.Sha256Hash;
007import org.bitcoinj.script.Script;
008import org.consensusj.bitcoin.json.conversion.HexUtil;
009
010/**
011 * UTXO Info object from Bitcore/Omni {@code getaddressutxos}.
012 */
013public class AddressUtxoInfo {
014    private final Address address;
015    private final Sha256Hash txid;
016    private final int outputIndex;
017    private final Script script;
018    private final Coin satoshis;
019    private final int height;
020    private final boolean coinbase;
021
022    public AddressUtxoInfo(@JsonProperty("address")     Address address,
023                           @JsonProperty("txid")        Sha256Hash txid,
024                           @JsonProperty("outputIndex") int outputIndex,
025                           @JsonProperty("script")      String script,
026                           @JsonProperty("satoshis")    long satoshis,
027                           @JsonProperty("height")      int height,
028                           @JsonProperty("coinbase")    boolean coinbase) {
029        this.address = address;
030        this.txid = txid;
031        this.outputIndex = outputIndex;
032        this.script = Script.parse(HexUtil.hexStringToByteArray(script));
033        this.satoshis = Coin.ofSat(satoshis);
034        this.height = height;
035        this.coinbase = coinbase;
036    }
037
038    public Address getAddress() {
039        return address;
040    }
041
042    public Sha256Hash getTxid() {
043        return txid;
044    }
045
046    public int getOutputIndex() {
047        return outputIndex;
048    }
049
050    public Script getScript() {
051        return script;
052    }
053
054    public Coin getSatoshis() {
055        return satoshis;
056    }
057
058    public int getHeight() {
059        return height;
060    }
061
062    public boolean isCoinbase() {
063        return coinbase;
064    }
065}
